{"tid":1879682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔離令大漏洞 繼續自出自入支那疫阜","createTime":"2020-02-14T10:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T10:58:57.000Z","uid":80934,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34df04a10a0e4c65730f09ad699e5b4c01d7fb02","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"規例講到明<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 經港珠澳大橋由澳門嚟香港唔視為內地入境 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔受強制檢疫令所限</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輕鬆走入社區散播病毒</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imMi2bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimMi2bf.png&h=ce353a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202406e/cs22020240612.pdf?fbclid=IwAR3Jo5xgxxq1GR0av_2gAP6XNLHD5Wvqs2G0ExUzdwArxRKB6WeqgQI1qGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202406e%2Fcs22020240612.pdf%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Jo5xgxxq1GR0av_2gAP6XNLHD5Wvqs2G0ExUzdwArxRKB6WeqgQI1qGc&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=4be59c25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202406e/cs22020240612.pdf?fbclid=IwAR3Jo5xgxxq1GR0av_2gAP6XNLHD5Wvqs2G0ExUzdwArxRKB6WeqgQI1qGc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門往珠海嘅關口依然中門大開畀人自出自入支那疫阜<br />\n愛國小粉紅只要經澳門上珠海<br />\n就可以繼續上大陸食山珍野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返嚟香港唔使隔離 直入社區分享國產病毒🦠<br />\n第25單咪就係由港珠澳大橋輸入<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507291-20200207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507291-20200207.htm&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=4a9af0c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507291-20200207.htm&h=f8a80c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507291-20200207.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共話只要發現護照顯示入境者去過內地就要強制檢疫<br />\n但係去澳門只要身分證 上大陸只要回鄉證<br />\n佢又點知你有無上過大陸</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔全面封關根本係由得病毒喺社區散播</span></span>"},{"pid":"8a9c14155f393cc53b43666239619b15a87d730b","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:36:40.000Z","msg":"康"},{"pid":"e1dd0e0bfd9f7b7aeb1ccb83bda54a91317c436b","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"3f1d3d655958ac0d546e49825e1eecd63578280d","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:37:06.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"92c78f9ef7c5989aa05e9c281c1df92d267a27f2","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"311460540c9ea17b80e0ae75126c8a8e88892cac","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"683e623b485491be73139c6d836692680997b331","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"39a94dcb56025063d83d709f11431620abbd4e47","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"抗"},{"pid":"f6a82f5984e15c82c996d0cc936bc29cc45f738b","tid":1879682,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f98c96e8ae67707cf0f4c6b35d0fdcad9da31c9","tid":1879682,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"澳門仲難入"},{"pid":"9e4e01fdac08152fb8a8bfdd45856a300d7ca4f1","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"疫"},{"pid":"e17d56f8f4ffa4df2389cfc4abb7810e707bdb1d","tid":1879682,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"629e485783538f6c23456f5ed98545a5fe1bfeb6","tid":1879682,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBEc6HA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBEc6HA.png&h=fe362069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4cBOV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4cBOV0.png&h=46b13f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s7qcnf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs7qcnf0.png&h=d764631d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n往來澳門珠海既口岸唔封關 然後港珠澳大橋仲通到落黎香港 根本就係個極大既漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975cd5ab0cffdc11d18ccc4de06331a4cbb27158","tid":1879682,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0dfcb57f1843f8d62518c96a93f70ce1e20db12","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f98c96e8ae67707cf0f4c6b35d0fdcad9da31c9","tid":1879682,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"澳門仲難入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"仲有港珠澳大橋巴士 去澳門每半個鐘一班"},{"pid":"08ff7a816b2c415bbfaacc82f2fcbc9551f428b3","tid":1879682,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"全面封關 刻不容緩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5107bd0b9067e12c3289ab495aadd86387f60d","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"繼續推<br />\n唔全面堵截關口根本嘥氣<br />\n靠人誠實自律答你有冇上過大陸<br />\n就唔使你監控立法啦"},{"pid":"61e70662faa3d23b887642371d7e788330c5c2dc","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"都唔知有幾多病毒感染者以呢個方法入境<br />\n無經過檢疫<br />\n社區爆發都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"411231056fda02b5bbcadea0d19983392718ffa4","tid":1879682,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"cf18a7dc27285bd93bffded04c0d5cca596b833c","tid":1879682,"uid":80934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"眼見藍絲親戚打算鑽漏洞上珠海<br />\n返嚟唔使隔離繼續周圍走真係睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}